                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to a pawnbroker. I have a sheet, which I know was pawned by the prisone and a blanket, which I am not certain who pawned.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by MR. PHILLIPS. Q. Did you know her before? A. No, but I am certain she is the person.</p>
               <p>
            
